{"tid":2255083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"霆鋒再獲封「米芝蓮之友」 創新中餐搶盡風頭","createTime":"2020-10-23T09:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T10:08:19.000Z","uid":328383,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5d0fb1c4f0d995ecfa0b90bc9f0f391214697c","tid":2255083,"uid":328383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XEhuE3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXEhuE3M.jpg&h=9dd24043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒近年主攻大陸市場，又做多個音樂節目導師，其廚男形象更深入民心，今晚他獲安排出席上海米芝蓮指南2021晚宴，他示範了「五彩斑斕油潑麵」，有指這是他為米芝蓮晚宴特別獻技的創新中餐。從網民分享的短片看到，霆鋒親手在麵糰上放上裝飾，經製麵機壓製後做出色彩繽紛的麵條。<br />\n<br />\n霆鋒在自己的微博留言講解新菜色：「這次在傳統美食上做了點新嘗試，分解湖南特色剁椒魚中的辣，滾油澆製後的魚鱗立起來很像座小山，從入口酥脆的魚鱗到爆漿爽辣的魚籽，層次感很『炸』。陝西油潑麵加了五彩斑斕的葉菜，原來的配角也能散發主角光環。希望創新能吸引更多西方食客及年輕人，我們中華料理真的很了不起，有無限的發揮空間。做菜也太好玩了！」<br />\n而霆鋒今晚再獲認證其廚藝造詣，他獲大會再度頒發「米芝蓮之友」殊榮，今次是他繼2016年後，再度獲頒此殊榮，而且是4年兩度獲封、全球唯一一位不開餐廳也能得獎的米芝蓮名人廚師選手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Hi9N4l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Hi9N4l&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=7e14af4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Hi9N4l</a>"},{"pid":"a9963b86ec6eec715a05f921ad2e0a7346e50c51","tid":2255083,"uid":328383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"霆鋒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce553310c951a098dbb457ab1add34dfd786402","tid":2255083,"uid":111088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔表現fing蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96d475b980f5302602aedf157169415e50ae621","tid":2255083,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"從入口酥脆的魚鱗到爆漿爽辣的魚籽，層次感很『炸』。陝西油潑麵加了五彩斑斕的葉菜，原來的配角也能散發主角光環。希望創新能吸引更多西方食客及年輕人，我們中華料理真的很了不起，有無限的發揮空間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢段野咁食神feel<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n刻骨銘心豬骨"},{"pid":"cbdee4bc43c45a61b7c3c1012dc19322e31f4a3f","tid":2255083,"uid":49669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ce553310c951a098dbb457ab1add34dfd786402","tid":2255083,"uid":111088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔表現fing蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"Fing蕉師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2031332d0e99d0e786f3668e48fd9471d2b77263","tid":2255083,"uid":37440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:38:50.000Z","msg":"狗都唔食"},{"pid":"21c09c7a4a433fd2b439d102c0ffe0135ec89f77","tid":2255083,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"點解咁似彩虹鮮花拔絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838d82ed9477e0e02c03132242daad45ff12bf4f","tid":2255083,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESOhO4k.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESOhO4k.gif&h=743bd951&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff351d7287565c32cff961531ccb7adffdfdd0eb","tid":2255083,"uid":2784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:46:52.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係用生命黎演戲"},{"pid":"48ececa1beeb008318ee63795aab31f92cf6952a","tid":2255083,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ce553310c951a098dbb457ab1add34dfd786402","tid":2255083,"uid":111088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔表現fing蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"